hopobject.body: I'm not working at the moment maxidus generico In 1973 I was a consultant in the petroleum industry. One of my clients decided he would get his own oil through contacts in the Middle East and bring it to the East Coast to be refined for his exclusive use. He was able to procure a tanker full of oil but on arrival here in the USA he was not able to off load the oil because there was no storage capacity available, everything was full. This should tell you a lot about the so called oil shortage of 1973. It brought in a new era of high oil prices.
